  "_note": "Balancer V3 CompositeLiquidityRouter v2.permitBatchAndCall(...) \u2014 selector 0x19c6989f, contract 0xb21A277466e7dB6934556a1Ce12eb3F032815c8A. Same wrapper as the Router/BatchRouter pbc but on the CompositeLiquidityRouter: bundles Permit2 approvals with a multicall of Composite self-calls (chiefly addLiquidityProportionalToERC4626Pool / removeLiquidityProportionalFromERC4626Pool). Decoded via multicall_recurse over multicallData \u2014 each child re-enters the route against the Composite address and resolves via balancer_v3:composite_pool_tokens. The bundled permit2Batch grant is not separately surfaced (same as the other pbc manifests). Mainnet only.",
